\u0123is Pu\u010dinskis]]\n|2012-05-18\n|-\n|[[FK Spartaks J\u016brmala|Spartaks J\u016brmala]]\n|{{flagicon|Latvia}} [[O\u013cegs Blagonade\u017edins]]\n|Sacked\n|2012-07-20\n|4th\n|{{flagicon|Lithuania}} [[Arminas Narbekovas]]\n|2012-07-23\n|}\n\n== Broadcasting ==\nJust as last season most of the matches are transmitted live via ''sportacentrs.com'' online and sportacentrs TV channel.<ref name=\"sportacentrs\">{{cite web|url=http://sportacentrs.com/sportacentrs_tv/|title=Sportacentrs TV \u2013 Sportacentrs.com|publisher=sportacentrs.com|accessdate=1 December 2015}}</ref> In June 2012 broadcasting rights were also bought by the English company [[Bet365]].<ref name=\"kasjauns\">{{cite web|url=http://www.kasjauns.lv/lv/zinas/83562/pirmo-reizi-vesture-pardotas-latvijas-virsligas-futbola-cempionata-interneta-translaciju-tiesibas|title=Pirmo reizi v\u0113stur\u0113 p\u0101rdotas Latvijas virsl\u012bgas futbola \u010dempion\u0101ta interneta transl\u0101ciju ties\u012bbas &#124; Kasjauns.lv|publisher=kasjauns.lv|accessdate=1 December 2015}}</ref> Since 2012 league's homepage ''futbolavirsliga.lv'' has been active and since September 2012 this website has been accompanied by InStat Football system, showing information and analysis of each match individually.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/780-virsliga-plano-ieviest-kvalitativu-statistikas-un-analizes-sistemu |title=Archived copy |access-date=2012-09-22 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130219030923/http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/780-virsliga-plano-ieviest-kvalitativu-statistikas-un-analizes-sistemu |archive-date=2013-02-19 |url-status=dead }}</ref> Since October 2012 Virsl\u012bga has also had its own analytical broadcast after each round of matches with football experts discussing about the games and future events connected to Latvian football. Its transmitted via sportacentrs TV.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/1061-virsligai-savs-apskata-raidijums |title=Archived copy |access-date=2012-11-11 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130218233647/http://futbolavirsliga.lv/index.php/jaunumi/1061-virsligai-savs-apskata-raidijums |archive-date=2013-02-18 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n== League table ==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n\n|team1=DGD|name_DGD=[[FC Daugava|Daugava Daugavpils]]\n|team2=SKO|name_SKO=[[Skonto FC|Skonto]]\n|team3=VEN|name_VEN=[[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]]\n|team4=LIE|name_LIE=[[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]]\n|team5=SPJ|name_SPJ=[[FK Spartaks J\u016brmala|Spartaks J\u016brmala]]\n|team6=FCJ|name_FCJ=[[FC J\u016brmala|J\u016brmala]]\n|team7=JEL|name_JEL=[[FK Jelgava|Jelgava]]\n|team8=MLU|name_MLU=[[FS METTA/Latvijas Universit\u0101te|METTA/LU]]\n|team9=DGR|name_DGR=[[FK Daugava (2003)|Daugava R\u012bga]]\n|team10=GUL|name_GUL=[[FB Gulbene]]\n|win_DGD=23|draw_DGD=9|loss_DGD=4|gf_DGD=64|ga_DGD=25|status_DGD=C\n|win_SKO=21|draw_SKO=11|loss_SKO=4|gf_SKO=58|ga_SKO=22\n|win_VEN=23|draw_VEN=5|loss_VEN=8|gf_VEN=63|ga_VEN=22\n|win_LIE=21|draw_LIE=7|loss_LIE=8|gf_LIE=60|ga_LIE=33\n|win_SPJ=13|draw_SPJ=10|loss_SPJ=13|gf_SPJ=61|ga_SPJ=56\n|win_FCJ=10|draw_FCJ=9|loss_FCJ=17|gf_FCJ=47|ga_FCJ=49\n|win_JEL=7|draw_JEL=10|loss_JEL=19|gf_JEL=32|ga_JEL=56\n|win_MLU=7|draw_MLU=8|loss_MLU=21|gf_MLU=39|ga_MLU=82\n|win_DGR=5|draw_DGR=12|loss_DGR=19|gf_DGR=42|ga_DGR=79|status_DGR=O\n|win_GUL=5|draw_GUL=9|loss_GUL=22|gf_GUL=28|ga_GUL=70|status_GUL=R\n\n|col_CL2=green1|text_CL2=Qualification for [[2013\u201314 UEFA Champions League#Second qualifying round|Champions League second qualifying round]]\n|result1=CL2\n|col_EL1=blue1|text_EL1=Qualification for [[2013\u201314 UEFA Europa League#First qualifying round|Europa League first qualifying round]]\n|result2=EL1|result4=EL1\n|col_EL1b=blue1|text_EL1b=Qualification for [[2013\u201314 UEFA Europa League#First qualifying round|Europa League first qualifying round]] \n|note_res_EL1b=Winners of the [[2012\u201313 Latvian Footba