ava]]\n|18\n|-\n|2\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Y\u014dsuke Sait\u014d (footballer)|Y\u014dsuke Saito]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FB Gulbene]]/[[FK Ventspils]]\n|15\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|3\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|COL}} [[David Armero Cort\u00e9s|David Cort\u00e9s]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Spartaks J\u016brmala]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|12\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|LAT}} [[Daniils Turkovs]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Ventspils]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|5\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|LAT}} [[Antons Jeme\u013cins]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Spartaks J\u016brmala]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|11\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|LTU}} [[Tadas Labukas]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Skonto FC]]\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|LAT}} [[Val\u0113rijs \u0160abala]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Skonto FC]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"|7\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Nigeria}} [[Stanley Ibe]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FC Daugava]]\n|rowspan=\"6\"|10\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|LAT}} [[Val\u0113rijs Afanasjevs]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|SK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]]\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|LAT}} [[Vladimirs Kame\u0161s]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|SK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]]\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Latvia}} M\u0101rti\u0146\u0161 Mila\u0161\u0113vi\u010ds\n|align=\"left\"|[[FS Metta/Latvijas Universit\u0101te|FS Metta/LU]]\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Ghana}} [[Patrick Twumasi]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Spartaks J\u016brmala]]\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Latvia}} [[Vit\u0101lijs Zi\u013cs]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Daugava (2003)|FK Daugava R\u012bga]]\n|}\n\n==Player of the Month==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Month\n!Player\n!Club\n|-\n|March/April<ref name=\"Edmunds Novickis\">{{cite web |url=http://sportacentrs.com/futbols/lmt_virsliga/07052012-virsligas_marta_aprila_labakais_speletajs |title=Virsl\u012bgas marta/apr\u012b\u013ca lab\u0101kais sp\u0113l\u0113t\u0101js Saito, treneris - Pahars |author=Edmunds Novickis |date=2012-05-07 |publisher= Sportacentrs.com}}</ref>\n|{{flagic